data.description: This home is in PROBATE and purchase is subject to Court Approval.  Property is being sold in AS IS Condition.  See documents under the D Button.    Enjoy wild horses passing by your property and see the beautiful mountain and valley views!  This home features a split floor plan with a large suite off the master bedroom.  The kitchen has a small breakfast bar and island and opens into the dining room and living room areas.  Front and back decks and full back yard fencing are included. Partially landscaped, there are sprinklers to the plantings in the front and back yards.  Lot is 1.31 Acres. There is one bedroom that was converted into a ham radio room with the antenna still on the home.  SALE IS SUBJECT TO COURT APPROVAL.  COURT DATE FRIDAY 3/15 10 AM  26 SOUTH B ST 2ND FLOOR, STOREY COUNTY COURTHOUSE VIRGINIA CITY
